               "  Best balance of speed and reliability.\n\n" +
               "CHoCHOnly:\n" +
               "  Flip immediately on any CHoCH. Fastest but noisiest.\n" +
               "  Good for scalping or very active markets.\n\n" +
               "CHoCHThenBOS:\n" +
               "  CHoCH sets a 'pending' flip, confirmed only when\n" +
               "  a BOS follows in the same direction. Most conservative.\n\n" +
               "CHoCHThenBOS+EMA:\n" +
               "  Same as above, but EMA must also align on the\n" +
               "  confirming BOS bar. Maximum confirmation.",
     group = grpBias)

requireBarClose = input.bool(true, "Require Bar Close (Non-Repaint)",
